beer.beer_description:
Superdelic | Motueka

We've started putting our recent hazy learnings into action, aiming for thick haze, pillowy mouthfeel and balanced flavour. We're also bringing back Superdelic – remember how it absolutely sang in Squigglin’ and Doodlin’ from the old days? Still can't quite put our finger on what makes it so good, but we're into it!
